                     <msItem xml:id="p1_i1">
                        <locus from="2r" to="31v" facs="f9">Fols 2r–31v</locus>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3179Revela">Revelation of
                                                  John</title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           <hi rend="rubric">ዘዮሐንስ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ዘቈ</hi>ስጥንጥንያ፡ 
                  መጥሮ<hi rend="rubric">ጶሊስ፡ አ</hi>
                           <add place="above">መ፡ ሀ</add>
                           <hi rend="rubric">ለዎ፡ ይስድድ፡</hi> ራዕዩ፡ ለዮሐንስ፡ 
                ዘከመ፡ 
                ርእዮ፡ ለኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ። ዘወሀቦ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ከመ፡ ያርእዮሙ፡ ለአግብርቲሁ፡ ዘሀሎ፡ ይኩን፡ ፍጡነ።</incipit>
                        <explicit xml:lang="gez">ተፈጸመ፡ ራዕየ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ አብ፡ ቀለምሲስ፡ ዘውእቱ፡ ብሂል፡ ዘርእየ፡ በህይወቱ፡ ራዕየ፡
              ወተጽሕፈ፡ ለአቡሁ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ለገብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ራዕየ፡ ዮሐንስ።</explicit>
                        <note>There is a preliminary note to the text:
                <q xml:lang="gez">
                              <hi rend="rubric">በሰ፯ሰዓት፡ ይትጋብዑ፡</hi> ሕዝብ፡ ኀበ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስ<hi rend="rubric">ቲያን፡ በዐቢይ፡ ፍሥሐ፡</hi> ይእቲ፡ ዕለት።
              ለኵሉ፡ ሕዝብ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ወያብርሁ፡ ፯፡ ማኅትው፡ ወይእጥኑ፡ ካህናት፡ በ፯፡ ማዕጠንታት፡ እስከ፡ ይትነበብ፡ አቡ፡ ቀለምሲስ፡
              ወእምድኅሬሁ፡ የንብብ፡ ቀሲስ፡ ዘየአምር፡ መጽሐፈ፡ አርአያ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ በዐቢይ፡ ቃል። ወኢትግበሩ፡ ጥምቀተ፡ 
              ዘእንበለ፡ ዕለተ፡ ፍሲካ፡ ነግህ።</q>
                        </note>
                        <note>The text generally agrees with that of <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/CJRDF5NJ"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Platt1830novum"/><title level="m">Novum testamentum domini nostri et servatoris Jesu Christi aethiopice</title><editor><forename>Thomas Pell</forename><surname>Platt</surname></editor><pubPlace>Londini</pubPlace><publisher>Impressit Ricardus Watts</publisher><date>1830</date><note type="url">https://archive.org/details/novumtestamentu00platgoog</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Manuscripts</note><note type="tag">New Testament</note><note type="tag">bm:Platt1830novum</note></note><note type="tag">Manuscripts</note><note type="tag">New Testament</note><note type="tag">bm:Platt1830novum</note></bibl>.</note>
                        <note>The chapter divisions are the same as in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet41#ms_i2.1"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: BNFet41#ms_i2.1</span></ref>:
             
